title: Gaia Young - Wikispooks
cleaned_text:
Gaia Young, half-sister of Toby Young and daughter of Lord Michael Young reportedly died of a "headache during a heatwave" on 21 July 2021.[1] This was only reported by commercially-controlled media in September.

During COVID-19, she volunteered for the Islington Covid-19 taskforce, supporting people who had to shield, and cooking and bringing food to the homeless.[2]

On the day of her death she took a bike ride, bought some vintage clothes and had a friend over for dinner. Later that evening she excused herself and lay down on a sofa in the front room. She thought she was suffering from heatstroke. She was later rushed to University College London Hospital. Her condition deteriorated. 16 hours later she was declared brain dead.[3]

Most commercially-controlled media reported on her sudden death in early September 2021,[4][5][6] some did so much later.[7]

Most Commercially-controlled media made no mention of whether she had had a "COVID-19 vaccine". The Daily Star reported that she had her second one in March 2020.[8]
